videos.description: Duke's Frank Jackson connects on a three from the top of the key.
videos.headline: Jackson nothing but net on a three

videos.description: Clemson's Donte Grantham tosses an alley oop for Jaron Blossomgame, who catches and dunks.
videos.headline: Blossomgame skies for the slam

videos.description: Duke swings the ball around and finds Luke Kennard at the top of the key who buries a three.
videos.headline: Great ball movement sets up a Kennard 3-pointer

videos.description: Jaron Blossomgame strips Grayson Allen of the ball, they lays it in on the other end.
videos.headline: Blossomgame strips Allen then scores

videos.description: Luke Kennard cuts into the lane and gives a great  pass to Amile Jefferson, who scores and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Kennard's great wraparound pass allows Jefferson to score

videos.description: Clemson's Shelton Mitchell attacks the paint and finishes past a couple Duke defenders.
videos.headline: Mitchell attacks and scores

videos.description: Clemson's Shelton Mitchell tosses to Elijah Thomas who slams it in to help Clemson cut the deficit against Duke.
videos.headline: Transition slam cuts the Clemson deficit

videos.description: Clemson's Shelton Mitchell sprints past Grayson Allen to score and draw a foul.
videos.headline: Mitchell sprints by Allen for the score

videos.description: Clemson inbounds down 2 points, but can't get a shot off as time expires and Duke holds on to win.
videos.headline: Clemson can't get a shot off and Duke holds on to win
